Field Required Type Description
status required StreetViewStatus The status of the request.See StreetViewStatus for more information.
copyright optional string An array of snapped points.
date optional string A string indicating year and month that the panorama was captured.
location optional LatLngLiteral The location of the panorama.See LatLngLiteral for more information.
pano_id optional string A specific panorama ID. These are generally stable, though panoramas may change ID over time as imagery is refreshed.
